TITLE: Using Public Imports for Transitioning Proto Files
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use 'import public' to create placeholder files when moving proto definitions to new locations. This allows clients to continue importing the old location while transitioning to the new structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protocolbuffers.github.io/blob/main/content/programming-guides/proto3.md#2025-04-11_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: proto
CODE:
```
// new.proto
// All definitions are moved here
```

LANGUAGE: proto
CODE:
```
